WEBVTT

00:00:29.680 --> 00:00:32.415
grabbed with no concern for consent,

00:00:32.439 --> 00:00:35.056
no laws made for the men
that enforced them.

00:00:35.080 --> 00:00:37.496
We were trained to dodge,

00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:40.136
to wait, to cower and cover,

00:00:40.160 --> 00:00:43.056
to wait more, still, wait.

00:00:43.080 --> 00:00:44.960
We were told to be silent.

00:00:45.440 --> 00:00:47.696
But speak to your girls of this wartime,

00:00:47.720 --> 00:00:50.296
a year preceded by a score of the same,

00:00:50.320 --> 00:00:52.576
so as in two decades before,

00:00:52.600 --> 00:00:54.136
we wiped our eyes,

00:00:54.160 --> 00:00:56.056
laced caskets with flags,

00:00:56.080 --> 00:00:58.256
evacuated the crime scene of the club,

00:00:58.280 --> 00:00:59.576
caterwauled in the street,

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:02.896
laid our bodies on the concrete
against the outlines of our fallen,